46:["$","h2","69",{"className":"text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4","children":"Conclusion"}]
47:["$","p","70",{"className":"text-gray-700 leading-relaxed my-4","children":"Physical fences are the most reliable, zero-technology solution—ideal for homeowners wanting permanent, maintenance-free containment. GPS virtual fences offer flexibility, portability, and lower upfront costs—perfect for renters or owners wanting real-time tracking."}]
